description: Packed with vegetables and umami flavours, this Asian noodle soup recipe is quick and easy, making it a delicious midweek meal go-to.
name: Asian Noodle Soup Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 2 tbs pickled ginger and 1 tbs sesame seeds, toasted

recipeInstructions.text: Add noodles, mushroom, broccolini, buk choy and spinach and cook for 2 minutes or until softened. Ladle soup into bowls and garnish with pickled ginger and sesame seeds.
